The Wollmux is an extension for [http://www.openoffice.org OpenOffice.org] / [http://www.documentfoundation.org LibreOffice] developed by the [http://www.muenchen.de/int/en City Administration of Munich]. WollMux adds functions to OpenOffice.org / LibreOffice, to make the handling of templates, forms and letterheads much easier. Because WollMux is OpenSource and available for everyone, it is also used by other public administrative bodies and corporations.

